<% provide(:title, "About") %>
<%= stylesheet_link_tag "help.css" %>
<h1>About</h1>
<hr>
<p>
  edxUCLA is a site where students can connect with tutors, schedule meetings and learn different subjects. 
  For questions on how to navigate the site, please refer to the help page. For additional questions, feel free
  to contact us by filling the form below: <br><br><br><br>
  <form id="contact_form" action="javascript:myFunction(); return false;" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
	<div class="row">
		<label for="name">Your name:</label><br />
		<input id="name" class="input" name="name" type="text" value="" size="30" /><br />
	</div>
	<div class="row">
		<label for="email">Your email:</label><br />
		<input id="email" class="input" name="email" type="text" value="" size="30" /><br />
	</div>
	<div class="row">
		<label for="message">Your message:</label><br />
		<textarea id="message" class="input" name="message" rows="7" cols="30"></textarea><br />
	</div>
	<input id="submit_button" type="submit" value="Send email" />
  </form>						
</p>